Unnamed: 6: Skyhigh Enterprise Browser Security - AddOn (Germany Data Center)

Band:
Skyhigh NON GA QUOTES ONLY
Skyhigh Security SKUs are limited to Skyhigh Security Authorized Distributors Only.

Range:
Skyhigh Enterprise Browser Security - AddOn
LICENSE: Per User.
DELIVERABLE: Activation via email.
PRODUCT CONTENT: This product offers Enterprise Browser Security to any type of modern browsers (Bring your own browser) on any type of device (Bring your own device) offering browser-based security controls such as Clickjacking protection, Cookie theft protection, Session jacking protection and DLP controls such as Clipboard protection, Sensitive data masking, Watermarking with user details, Upload/download/login protection.
It is an add-on to MVW, MVW-ADV, MPA, SSEFW, SSEFWB, UCEB, UCEA, UCEC SKUs that is configurable by policy.
PRODUCT REQUIREMENT: This is an add-on SKU. Customer must have an entitlement of MVW, MVW-ADV, MPA, SSEFW, SSEFWB, UCEB, UCEA, UCEC SKUs.
